 This install applies to "Guy Spy" © 1989 ReadySoft (4 disks).
                        "Guy Spy CDTV" © 1993 ReadySoft.

 If you have problems with this installation please try and get a newer
 version of this package from the WHDLoad WWW-Page. If that doesn't help try
 some Tooltypes like NOCACHE, NOAUTOVEC, NOVBRMOVE, NOMMU, PAL or NTSC. If
 that also fails, please inform the author via the Bug-Report-Form which
 can be accessed on the WHDLoad WWW-Page or create a mantis issue directly
 at http://mantis.whdload.de

 For the full WHDLoad package, other installs and updates refer to:
   http://www.whdload.de/
 or   aminet:dev/misc/whdload#?
 and  aminet:game/patch/


*********************************************************************************
************************* original 4 disks version ******************************
*********************************************************************************

 This install requires WHDLoad and RawDIC to be in the path. Both can be found
 in the WHDLoad package.
 To install from a different drive than DF0: select installation mode Expert.

 The installed program requires 0.5 MB ChipMem and 0.5 MB OtherMem.
 It can be quit by pressing F10 (key can be changed with Tooltype "QuitKey=").

 version 1.0 (17.03.02) done by C-Fou!:
 - New install script for CDTV and 4 Disks version
 - rawdic imager used
 - Nightmare decrypt routines fixed
 - Some access faults fixed
 - Tooltype CUSTOM1 used (CUSTOM1=1: F2 to active cheat menu like 'ROVENA')
 - Tooltype CUSTOM2 used too (CUSTOM2=1: F1 to skip screen like 'GETVONMAXGUY')
 - Load/Save game position redirected to HD in 'GuySpy.save' 

In game Keys:
L : Load game position (Green Screen)
S : Save game position (Red Screen)
P : pause

Known Bug:
Using ROVENA cheat menu if you choose to start by SKY pert game crashes! (like on disk)

                   < Thank to Chris VELLA for original game. >


*********************************************************************************
******************************* CDTV version ************************************
*********************************************************************************

 The installed program requires 0.8 MB ChipMem and 0.5 MB OtherMem.
 It can be quit by pressing num '*' (key can be changed with Tooltype "QuitKey=").

 Install-Script & HD-loader © 2002-2004 JOTD

 History:

 v2.0 (20.11.04):
 - adapted to WHDLoad v16

 v1.0 (2002): initial release
 - Runs fully from HD using WHDLoad/KickEmu/KickDOS
 - Save game to HD (bookmark.device emulated)
 - Convenient install script
 - Quit key (numerical '*', or configurable with QUITKEY)
 - Nice icons by Exoticons and CFou!
 - Documentation included

 Requirements:

  The game requires a installed A1200 Kickstart 1.3 image.
  The kickstart image must be located in the directory "Devs:Kickstarts" and
  must be named "kick34005.A500". The image can be extracted from a A500 with
  tools like 'GrabKick' or similar which can be found on aminet.
  If the image is of wrong version or altered in any way WHDLoad will quit with
  a appropriate requester.
  Additionally the file "kick34005.A500.RTB" must be installed in the same
  directory as the kickstart image. It can be found in the archive
  "util/boot/skick345.lha" on aminet.


